## Permissions

```json
{
  "permissions": {
    "allow": ["Bash(git diff:*)", "Bash(npm run:*)"],
    "ask": ["Bash(git push:*)"],
    "deny": ["WebFetch", "Read(./.env)", "Read(./secrets/**)"],
    "additionalDirectories": ["../docs/"],
    "defaultMode": "acceptEdits"
  }
}
```

**Security**: Use `deny` to exclude sensitive files. Replaces deprecated `ignorePatterns`.

